    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for parts or as a major restoration project. The exterior shows significant wear, including several large dents, deep scratches, and advancing rust on the wheel arches and rocker panels. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and requires immediate attention, and the transmission shifts harshly between gears. The interior has seen better days, with visible tears in the upholstery and several non-functional electronic components. It is being sold strictly as-is, with no warranties expressed or implied.",
