    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and affordable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road? This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest wear from its travels but still offering a dependable driving experience! It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone who prioritizes functionality and value over a showroom finish. Come see why this practical car is a fantastic deal for its next owner!",
      "price": 21500.0,
